name: SSS_SEARCH_ERROR_OCCURRED
message:
Search error occurred: Failed to parse SQL [
 select top undefined
 transaction.id,
 transaction.tranid,
 transaction.entity,
 transaction.transactionnumber,
 transaction.currency,
 transaction.exchangerate,
 transactionline.foreignAmount,
 transactionline.netAmount,
 transaction.trandate,
 transaction.memo,
 transaction.custbody_lmry_document_type,
 transactionline.foreignAmountUnpaid,
 transactionline.expenseaccount,
 transaction.custbody_lmry_paymentmethod
 from
 transaction
 inner join transactionline on transactionline.transaction = transaction.id and transactionline.foreignAmountUnpaid > 0 and transactionline.mainline = 'T' and transactionline.subsidiary = 7 and transactionline.expenseaccount = 25 
 inner join vendor on vendor.id = transaction.entity 
 where
 transaction.type = 'VendBill'
 and 
 transaction.paymenthold = 'F'
 and
 transaction.currency = 7 and 
 
 transaction.trandate >= '1/1/2025' and 
 transaction.trandate <= '28/8/2025' 
 ORDER BY transaction.trandate DESC
 ]: syntax error, state:106(10102) near: undefined(2,24, token code:0)
